**2.1 Core Principles & Pacing**

Fireship videos follow a core philosophy: *\"Your goal is to make the
best YOUTUBE videos possible. Not the best produced videos. Not the
funniest videos. Not the highest quality videos. It\'s to make the best
YOUTUBE videos possible.\"*

**For techfren:** This means optimizing for the platform, not for
production perfectionism. A scrappier video that hooks viewers beats a
polished video nobody watches. Your \"discovery energy\" voice already
aligns with this---authenticity over production value.

