**Joke Placement Strategy**

-   **First joke within 15-20 seconds** (rewards viewers for clicking)

-   **Meme/joke every 20-30 seconds** (maintains entertainment value)

-   **Callback jokes** to earlier references (creates satisfying
    connections)

-   **End on a memorable line** (leaves viewers with positive feeling)

**Writing Techniques**

**Contrast Technique:** State something serious, then immediately
undercut it.

*\"This revolutionary AI will transform the industry. By making
developers obsolete. But hey, at least we\'ll have more time for
therapy.\"*

**Absurdist Escalation:** Start reasonable, escalate to ridiculous.

*\"They raised 100 million dollars to build\... a todo app. But this one
uses blockchain. And AI. And it runs on Kubernetes. In space.\"*

**Deadpan Observation:** State obvious absurdities as if reporting
facts.

*\"The company promises their framework will solve all your problems.
Which is exactly what the last 47 frameworks promised.\"*

